# SECURITY BEST PRACTICES:
# ✓ Use strong, unique passwords
# ✓ Never share your secrets.yaml file
# ✓ Never commit secrets.yaml to GitHub
# ✓ Back up secrets.yaml securely (encrypted)
# ✓ Change OTA password after sharing device temporarily
